    <item>
      <title>万科债券抛售表明债务偿还担忧加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/vanke-s-bond-selloff-signals-growing-worries-about-debt-payments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[万科企业股份有限公司长期以来被视为中国房地产市场的领头羊，但随着人们对其大量债务即将到期的担忧加剧，以及尽管政府出台了救助措施，但房地产危机依然根深蒂固，万科正面临日益加剧的债券抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/vanke-s-bond-selloff-signals-growing-worries-about-debt-payments</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 04:23:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
